{"word":"κεφαλή","slug":"κεφαλή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰεφαλή, ῆς, ἡ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ IE\">IE</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ assoc.\">assoc.</a>] <b>head<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> as anatomical term <b><a href='B:470 5:36'>Mt 5:36</a>; <a href='B:470 10:30'>10:30</a>; <a href='B:470 27:39'>27:39</a>; <a href='B:480 6:24'>Mk 6:24f</a>, 27f; <a href='B:490 7:38'>Lk 7:38</a>; <a href='B:500 13:9'>J 13:9</a>; <a href='B:510 21:24'>Ac 21:24</a>; <a href='B:520 12:20'>Ro 12:20</a>; <a href='B:530 11:4'>1 Cor 11:4f</a>; <a href='B:530 12:21'>12:21</a>; <a href='B:730 1:14'>Rv 1:14</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in Rv<b>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ transf.\">transf.</a> sense of a, as architectural extremity <b><a href='B:470 21:42'>Mt 21:42</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ par.\">par.</a> <b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp></b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ transf.\">transf.</a> sense of a, as directing agent within a ranking system <b><a href='B:530 11:3'>1 Cor 11:3</a>; <a href='B:560 1:22'>Eph 1:22</a>; <a href='B:560 5:23'>5:23</a>; <a href='B:580 1:18'>Col 1:18</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>d.</pp></b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ref.\">ref.</a> to political significance <b><a href='B:510 16:12'>Ac 16:12</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κεφαλαιόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κεφαλιόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}